{"tid":658776,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"非港身分證報考DSE人數急增逾兩倍　多名中國學生申聯招獲取錄","createTime":"2018-05-09T09:04:59.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-09T12:09:48.000Z","uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":16,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"a4fdcf0c7d9191299e56d78ae12365c7eb88d7af","tid":658776,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-09T09:04:59.000Z","msg":"一年一度的中學文憑試（DSE），是本地生入讀大學途徑之一。早前有報道指，內地高考大軍覬覦香港大學及文憑試，更有補習班助內地生考DSE報讀大學，引起憂慮。教育局稱，考評局沒有統計「非本地學生」報考DSE數字，但根據教育局資料，今年持「非香港身份證」報考人數，較去年急升逾兩倍。<br />\n<br />\n教育局長楊潤雄書面回覆教育界議員葉建源時表示，考評局不會收集與處理考務安排無關的個人資料，包括學生來源地，故該局沒有「非本地學生」報考文憑試統計數字，但若以身分證明文件統計，2014至2017年平均每年有數十人報考，平均報考逾3科，而2018年報考人數，更較2017年急升逾2倍，平均報考5.5科。<br />\n<br />\n持非香港身分證報考文憑試考生人數及報考科目如下：<br />\n<br />\n考試年份／報考人數／平均報考科目<br />\n<br />\n2018／184／5.5<br />\n<br />\n2017／55／5<br />\n<br />\n2016／42／4.2<br />\n<br />\n2015／41／3.7<br />\n<br />\n2014／44／3.3<br />\n<br />\n另外，過去5年（2013至2017）有68名非本地生以文憑試成績，透過聯招申請入讀資助學士學位課程，當中18人獲取錄，詳情如下：<br />\n<br />\n申請年份／獲取錄總人數／按大學劃分人數／按來源地劃分人數<br />\n<br />\n2017／10／中大（5），城大（3），港大（1），浸大（1）／中國內地（10）<br />\n<br />\n2016／4／嶺大（2），城大（1），中大（1）／中國內地（4）<br />\n<br />\n2015／2／城大（1），科大（1）／中國內地（2）<br />\n<br />\n2014／0／0／0<br />\n<br />\n2013／2／港大（1），理大（1）／澳門（1），越南（1）<br />\n<br />\n楊潤雄稱「非本地生」聯招入學申請，只會與其他非本地生非聯招入學申請一併考慮，校方不會把有關申請人，計算在本地學生學額內。"},{"pid":"988fbddec2712d2926169240c19f39906bd86276","tid":658776,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-09T09:05:09.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20180509/s00001/1525855061195\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20180509%2Fs00001%2F1525855061195&d=Wasgvqq%2BsjEdEnWNDSVYoFKzBYqMCiHg3GgvTcrvEuQ%3D&h=898da593\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20180509%2Fs00001%2F1525855061195&h=972f87f7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20180509/s00001/1525855061195</a>"},{"pid":"44750af276e629cec7beb211fe444a9d4ba94ab1","tid":658776,"uid":150685,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-09T09:33:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 蝗連DSE都要搶住黎考"},{"pid":"c2f4bdde2d47a16c5b62c191fe4a26a59885111a","tid":658776,"uid":40226,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-09T09:34:51.000Z","msg":"收皮啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7a9324dcbc2e56d5ac20bbf61c29103514212f18","tid":658776,"uid":71543,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-09T10:09:42.000Z","msg":"大量支那人湧入香港<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"50378c40b33d1a759fa05085eeb0742096cf8b68","tid":658776,"uid":93784,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-09T10:10:34.000Z","msg":"5毛同港豬話齋 公平競爭喎 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ec2fd432ea5b227ee484b667c13a6c0092d4cce0","tid":658776,"uid":11148,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-09T10:12:44.000Z","msg":"00後話冇問題,話香港係中國地方點解唔可以考dse<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8022a4a565e01aa382788069bdc78c26c3cdaed1","tid":658776,"uid":86841,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-09T10:17:24.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"aab4a50f92cc411870f40f7f2acb79b3aa104748","tid":658776,"uid":55924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8022a4a565e01aa382788069bdc78c26c3cdaed1","tid":658776,"uid":86841,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"ec2fd432ea5b227ee484b667c13a6c0092d4cce0","tid":658776,"uid":11148,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-